These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, motorbike
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, teacher
1. the mechanic is in an even position##4
2. the teacher is the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Transport   | motorbike | taxi |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, grey
1. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee        |
| Color      | brown  | grey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, davidoff
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Cigar   | davidoff    | old-henry |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, mango
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Game   | mah-jongg      | canasta |
| Food       | broccoli | mango    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
